{"title":"Kätepesu","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"organic-hand-wash-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Hand Wash 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic hand wash, specially designed to cleanse gently while leaving the hands soft and smooth.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of lavender (soothing), nettle (antioxidant) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Dispense into wet hands. Rinse thoroughly. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Citric Acid*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Sodium Lactate*, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e** certified organic (67,5%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49091863740743,"sku":null,"price":23.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-hand-wash-250ml-158204.jpg?v=1739897343"},{"product_id":"magrada-luxurious-bubble-hand-soap-400ml","title":"Magrada Luxurious Bubble Hand Soap 400ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn partnership with Mulligalerii, Magrada has developed a truly luxurious and enchanting product series that combines the opulent aromas of top-quality sparkling wine with gentle botanical extracts to deliver an enjoyable experience. Gypsum flower, aloe, wash acacia, and desert date form a nurturing quartet that provides rich care for your skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis exclusive hand soap caresses your senses while the silky soap foam cleanses and moisturizes your skin, leaving it soft and radiant. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply on hands, rinse with water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Aqua, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Citric Acid, Sodium Chloride, Parfum, Isostearamide MIPA, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Sodium Lactate, Sodium PCA, Glyceryl Laurate, Acacia Concinna (Shikakai) Fruit Extract, Balanites Aegyptiaca (Soapberry Tree) Fruit Extract, Gypsophila Paniculata (White Saponaria) Root Extract, Glycine, Fructose, Urea, Niacinamide, Inositol, Lactic Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid\\n \\nIngredients of natural origin: 95,33%\"}' data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":13057,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":12}'\u003eAqua, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Citric Acid, Sodium Chloride, Parfum, Isostearamide MIPA, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Sodium Lactate, Sodium PCA, Glyceryl Laurate, Acacia Concinna (Shikakai) Fruit Extract, Balanites Aegyptiaca (Soapberry Tree) Fruit Extract, Gypsophila Paniculata (White Saponaria) Root Extract, Glycine, Fructose, Urea, Niacinamide, Inositol, Lactic Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 95,33%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e vegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e EU allergen-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49583815131463,"sku":null,"price":25.8,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-luxurious-bubble-hand-soap-400ml-861222.png?v=1739897260"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-hand-wash-refill-500ml","title":"Vielö Organic Hand Wash Refill 500ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic hand wash, specially designed to cleanse gently while leaving the hands soft and smooth.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of lavender (soothing), nettle (antioxidant) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy choosing sustainable refills you take good care of your skin and our planet. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Dispense into wet hands. Rinse thoroughly. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Citric Acid*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Sodium Lactate*, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** certified organic (67,5%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901114716487,"sku":null,"price":39.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-hand-wash-refill-500ml-257750.jpg?v=1739897189"},{"product_id":"madara-wild-woods-moisture-wash-500ml","title":"MÁDARA Wild Woods Moisture Wash 500ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eInfused with aromatic extracts of horsetail and absinthium, this heavenly scented moisture wash pays homage to Northern flora, capturing the freshness of wild woods.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe dermatologically tested formula has been crafted with natural physio-moisturisers, gently cleansing and hydrating the skin to leave it soft and supple. Formulated without harsh surfactants, synthetic fragrances and artificial colourants, it is suitable for both hands and body.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage and lather over damp skin, rinse well. Follow with MÁDARA hand or body cream of choice. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Sodium Coco-sulfate, Sodium cocoamphoacetate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Coco-glucoside, Citric acid, Aroma, Sodium PCA, Benzyl Alcohol, Aqua, Artemisia Absinthium (Absinthium) Herb Extract, Equisetum Arvense (Horsetail) Extract, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Linalool, Eugenol, Citral\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916960665927,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-wild-woods-moisture-wash-500ml-660570.jpg?v=1739897158"},{"product_id":"madara-bitter-honey-moisture-wash-500ml","title":"MÁDARA Bitter Honey Moisture Wash 500ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLather up and bathe in this heavenly scented body wash that captures the fragrant characteristics of dewy morning freshness, blooming meadowsweet and beautiful Northern summers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThoughtfully crafted with natural physio-moisturisers, the caring formula nourishes as it cleanses, leaving behind soft, supple skin and an enticing scent.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor use as a daily hand and body wash, it is dermatologically tested and free from harsh surfactants, synthetic fragrances and artificial colourants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage and lather over damp skin, rinse well. Follow with MÁDARA hand or body cream of choice.  \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Sodium Coco-sulfate, Sodium cocoamphoacetate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Citric acid, Coco-glucoside, Aroma, Benzyl Alcohol, Aqua, Sodium PCA, Sodium Benzoate, Spiraea Ulmaria (Meadowsweet) Flower Extract, Galium Verum (Lady's Bedstraw\/Madara) Extract, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Chloride, Linalool, Limonene, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil, Juniperus Virginiana Oil, Benzyl Salicylate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916993106247,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-bitter-honey-moisture-wash-500ml-849581.jpg?v=1739897182"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/katepesu.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}